data.description: **WOW** BIG Price Reduction - Seller may also help with some CLOSING COSTS!! First time ever on the market! Welcome home to Carlton Square; this lovely home in the heart of Inglewood and in a desirable gated community with 2 guard controlled access gates and on-site security patrols. The 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home has had many recent upgrades and improvements. The kitchen was completed in 2023: all new upper cabinets and pantry and lower cabinet doors, refinished countertops, new Amana range and a new stainless sink and faucet. Many improvements were done just 2 years ago: downstairs there is beautiful wood laminate flooring, tile flooring added in the bathrooms, the interior was painted, and the decorative fretwork was installed on the expansive living room wall and in 1 guest bedroom. In 2017, all the windows and sliding glass doors were replaced for energy efficiency. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms including an extra large primary bedroom with 2 closets, a double sink vanity and a shower in tub combo. Across the hall there is a full bathroom and 2 more spacious guest bedrooms. The 2 car garage features tons of storage cabinets and laundry area; washer and dryer are included. In the large private backyard there is a huge gazebo with lights, added in 2016 that is perfect for entertaining. Carlton Square HOA amenities include maintenance for your house roof, exterior paint & lawncare. You will also enjoy the use of two swimming pools, tennis courts, a basketball court, playground, and a clubhouse. Adjacent to the Kia Forum, SoFi Stadium; home of the RAMs and Chargers, and centrally located with proximity to Downtown LA, LAX, freeways, beaches, and other attractions. Don’t wait, make this your forever home now! Watch Virtual 360 tour for walk through.
